Welcome to an Unnamed LexiMUD!

Primary Rules:
  No transfering items between your characters
  No simultaneous multiplaying
  No harassment / bigotry (racism/sexism/etc)
  Only MILD (PG / PG-13) swearing is tolerated
Failure to follow rules will result in varying degrees of punishment,
including, but not limited to: warnings, muting, disconnection, purging,
freezing (locking your character), and, in extreme cases, banning.
Type POLICY in the game to see the core policies.  IGNORANCE IS NO EXCUSE!
NOTE: We act first, ask questions later.  You have been warned!
